{ Annotated by GM Axel Bachmann - https://lichess.org/@/ABachmann

The class between Pragg and Sindarov offered us, in my opinion, the most interesting game of the tournament so far. Both players showed their determination by getting into an extremely complicated position, with Sindarov finally scoring a gigantic win with the black pieces. }
